<table border="0" cellpadding="5" width="550" cellspacing="5" height="400" ><tr valign="top" height="400" ><td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" ><![CDATA[<div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font size="2"><font style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><br></font></font></div><div><font face="arial"><div style="font-size: small;">Hello {!Contact.FirstName},</div><div style="font-size: small;"><br></div><div style="font-size: small;">As a Fleet One EDGE customer, you can save up to <b>25%</b> with Imperial, a leading distributor of quality maintenance repair parts. You'll also enjoy:&nbsp;</div><div style="font-size: small;"><ul><li>Larger product selection at a lower cost than conventional brick and mortar stores<br><br></li><li>Same day shipping - place your order before 2pm EST, and it ships that same day<br><br></li><li>Shipping saver program - pay one flat fee of $49 and receive free ground shipping for one year on all orders over $100*<br><br></li><li>Flexible ordering options - place your order via the Imperial Mobile App, over the phone, or online at <a href="http://www.imperialsupplies.com/?utm_source=truckers-b2b&amp;utm_medium=webpage&amp;utm_campaign=imperial-home-page">imperialsupplies.com</a></li></ul></div><div style="font-size: small;"><br></div><div style="font-size: small;"><b>Get started:</b></div><div style="font-size: small;"><br></div><div style="font-size: small;">To start saving up to 25% with Imperial, please call me or reply to this email and let me know that you'd like your account linked to the EDGE discount. We will forward your information over to Imperial so they can create your account and attach the discount.</div><div style="font-size: small;"><br></div><div style="font-size: small;">Should you have any questions or would like more information, please don't hesitate to call me at 866.840.7115.</div><div style="font-size: small;"><br></div><div style="font-size: small;">Thank you,</div><div style="font-size: small;"><br></div><div style="font-size: small;">{!User.FirstName} {!User.LastName}&nbsp;</div><div style="font-size: small;">Fleet One EDGE Benefits</div><div style="font-size: small;">866.840.7115</div><div style="font-size: small;">benefits@fleetoneedge.com</div><div style="font-size: small;"><br></div><div style="font-size: small;"><br></div><div style="font-size: small;"><br></div><div><font size="1">Not applicable to customers who already have a special pricing program or national account established with Imperial Supplies. *Imperial Supplies Shipping Saver Offer applies to orders from Imperial shipped by ground method to the 48 contiguous states. This offer does not apply to special orders, express or international shipping, orders that require special handling and orders that include items shipped by motor freight. Imperial reserves the right to discontinue offering the Shipping Saver Offer to customers/prospects at any time. Cancellation and full refund of $49 will only be allowed if cancellation is requested before any qualifying product purchases have been made. Once any products have been shipped under the terms, no fees will be refunded.&nbsp;</font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><br></div></font><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial" size="4"><br></font></div></div>]]></td></tr></table>